 a good level of comfort. Colour schemes black and white but all are tasteful. Bathrooms are simply decorated but in excellent condition.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>This is a traditional Ottoman style building with Romanesque influences.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>The hotel is part of a famous chain called faros restaurants as well. In the hotel there is only one small cafe-bar but there is a restaurant of the chain within 5 minutes walking distance. The restaurants offer world and international cuisine.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>The lobby is very small as the building is an old ottoman era building but great modern design inside and it is connected with the cafe of the hotel.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Shower</Code><Text>Shower</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TelephoneInRoom</Code><Text>Direct Dial Telephone</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>30</Score><Description>Three star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>